            "type": "text",
            "text": "The BGE M3 model from BAAI is a leading multilingual embedding solution, and leveraging baai bge m3 python enables efficient integration into API infrastructures. This guide focuses on deploying the Bge_M3_FP16 variant in production, offering actionable insights for experienced API teams on setup, implementation, and optimization."
